lo</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">C. Méndez Díaz</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">E. Rodríguez García</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">R. Soler Fernández</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">A. Rois Siso</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">M. Marini Díaz</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2015Nov1 | Radiología, Vol. 57, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rx.2015.07.002">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.rxeng.2015.09.002"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rxeng.2015.09.002">Imaging findings in cardiac masses (Part i): Study protocol and benign tumors</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">C. Díaz Angulo</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">C. Méndez Díaz</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">E. Rodríguez García</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">R. Soler Fernández</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">A. Rois Siso</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">M. Marini Díaz</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2015Nov1 | Radiología (English Edition), Vol. 57, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.rxeng.2015.09.002">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.3892/ol.2015.3529"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.3892/ol.2015.3529">Surgical treatment of primary cardiac tumors in children: Experience of a single institute</a></div><div class="related_